Package jwiki.util Description

Miscellaneous classes and methods which support the jwiki core framework. These are fairly generic, and made available in their own package for general purpose use. Contains methods ranging from I/O, to String functions, to GUI. There are also tools/frameworks such as FLogin/WikiGen (which provide an interface to locally save login credentials and encrypt them).
